    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "I'm not sure we have docs for that (yet), and how recent this is, but if you do `<PathToPython> -m IPython kernelspec install-self --name MyVenvPython` you should get a kernel name `MyVenvPython`.\n\nYou can also create the kernelspec by hand, it in not too complicated, Just duplicate an existing one and edit the `kernel.json`\n"
